Phil Barker
Global Head of Sales
Phil joined Standard Life Investments as a sales director in 1998, becoming head of retail sales in 2003 and head of European business development in 2007. His previous roles included head of sales at Schroders Financial Management and sales director at M&G. He is an Associate of the Chartered Insurance Institute.

